  "3123410": {
    "name": "优米雅的炼金工房 ～追忆之炼金术士与幻创之地～",
    "steam_appid": 3123410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "无论结局如何，仍将与禁忌同行。<br><br>炼金术RPG《优米雅的炼金工房》描述了优米雅一行人正视自己的“记忆”、即便感到迷茫仍然向着自己坚信的道路前进的故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SYSTEM</h2>收集、战斗、創造——<br>与伙伴的旅程中充满各种“体验”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■在广阔的开放式地图上无拘无束尽情冒险</h2>在广袤无垠的未知大地上，运用各种动作及道具，用自己的双脚开拓探索未知的旅程。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/a881564a7878e3772afec9ef6f55d651.poster.avif?t=1760596453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/a881564a7878e3772afec9ef6f55d651.webm?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/a881564a7878e3772afec9ef6f55d651.mp4?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/cc394176d9a8675c0bb636d5870bd55e.poster.avif?t=1760596453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/cc394176d9a8675c0bb636d5870bd55e.webm?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/cc394176d9a8675c0bb636d5870bd55e.mp4?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■战斗<br>由“交战距离”和“道具”带来的多样化动作</h2>在即时进行的战斗中，瞬间判断将受到考验。<br>玩家可运用两种攻击距离，即“交战距离”，并在战斗中灵活切换技能来巧妙作战。<br>此外，调合出的道具会变化成剑或枪等形状用来攻击。这些道具可以反复使用，因此不要犹豫，放心使用它们击退阻挡前路的敌人吧。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/294f73000eb6792af464bb12496682a1.poster.avif?t=1760596453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/294f73000eb6792af464bb12496682a1.webm?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/294f73000eb6792af464bb12496682a1.mp4?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■调合<br>从交织的“玛那”所诞生的物品</h2>操控蕴藏在材料中的“玛那”，根据配方制作出全新的物品。所制作的物品在探索和战斗等各种场合中能发挥强大的力量。<br>物品所拥有的力量强度取决于调合时使用的材料，因此，需要准确选择材料，并仔细辨识其中蕴藏的玛那的力量。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/f1c241f7c228f0d3f11bc999c14d6ed9.poster.avif?t=1760596453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/f1c241f7c228f0d3f11bc999c14d6ed9.webm?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/f1c241f7c228f0d3f11bc999c14d6ed9.mp4?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■在原野制作道具并根据个人喜好打造据点！</h2>简易调合能制作各种道具，比如制作探索道具来开辟道路，或是能有效运用于战斗或调合的道具。<br>此外，建造据点时也可以根据自己的喜好制作或摆放家具。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/8e8d0f9a81419355a7d35edefc1f19ab.poster.avif?t=1760596453\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/8e8d0f9a81419355a7d35edefc1f19ab.webm?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123410/extras/8e8d0f9a81419355a7d35edefc1f19ab.mp4?t=1760596453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>阿拉迪斯帝国是位于某大陆上曾繁盛一时的国家。<br>炼金术曾经为阿拉迪斯带来他国望尘莫及的发展，然而阿拉迪斯却在突发的天灾异变下灭亡。<br><br>时光流逝，数百年后——<br>如今，炼金术被视为“招致灭亡的危险术法”，并成为“恶”与“禁忌”的代名词。<br><br>一名炼金术士踏上已成为杳无人烟之秘境的大陆。<br>炼金术士名为优米雅·利斯菲尔德，在三年前因为一场意外失去了母亲，也因此得知自己是炼金术士的后代，并对此抱持许多疑问。<br>阿拉迪斯为什么会灭亡？<br>为何炼金术会被视为“禁忌”？<br>炼金术真的是“恶”吗？<br>她深信那片大陆上一定沉睡着所有的真相——<br>为了追寻失落的历史，优米雅踏上了旅途。<br><br>※游戏画面取自开发中版本，与实际游戏内容可能有所差异。<br><br>----<br><strong>[Steam®追加内容]优米雅的炼金工房 背包组合</strong><br>可变更优米雅背包的颜色及芙拉米烟效的饰品组合。<br><br>【组合内容】<br>·优米雅专用饰品“芙拉米背包”<br>·优米雅专用饰品“回忆背包”<br>·芙拉米专用饰品“星烟漫漫”<br>·芙拉米专用饰品“璨烟袅袅”<br><br>※在解锁建装功能并设置试衣间后，即可使用本追加内容。",
